I believe [tensorflow::mutex](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/platform/mutex.h) is a traivial destructor. And [LoadDynamicLibrary](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/f2c163919f51657ec0684bf415b3821af1afdc4f/tensorflow/core/framework/load_library.cc#L46) has simlar code
```
Status LoadDynamicLibrary(const char* library_filename, void** result,
                          const void** buf, size_t* len) {
  static mutex mu(LINKER_INITIALIZED);
  static std::unordered_map<string, Library> loaded_libs;
  Env* env = Env::Default();
```

